701792f-a.title: Bronx: Shore Drive - Lafayette Avenue
701792f-a.text:
Shore Drive, east side, at Lafayette Ave. The frame building is occupied by the Verein deutsch-amerik. Waaserfreunde (Society of
German-American water friends).
August 25, 1935.
P. L. Sperr.
